

Ascenso MX

Apertura 2013 | Clausura 2014 | Promotion Playoff

Apertura 2013

Changes before season:

- Querétaro relegated from first level 2012-13 season was disolved
- Neza FC moved to Ciudad del Carmen (Delfines)
- Irapuato moved to Zacatepec (Zacatepec 1948)
- Veracruz moved to San Luis Potosí (Atlético San Luis)
- Titanes de Tulancingo 2011-12 Second Division champions (third level) moved 
    to Oaxaca (Alebrijes)
- Ballenas Galeana promoted from Second Division replaced Pumas Morelos (relegated)
 
Regular Stage | Playoff Stage

